1
00:00:01,034 --> 00:00:02,669
Oh, sure. It's always like this.

2
00:00:03,202 --> 00:00:05,481
You said I'd be the face and
you'd stay behind the scenes,

3
00:00:05,505 --> 00:00:07,073
but here I am, taking the heat for you.

4
00:00:16,116 --> 00:00:17,384
Hey Mingyan,

5
00:00:17,617 --> 00:00:20,286
wake up already.

6
00:00:25,658 --> 00:00:26,659
You

7
00:00:27,394 --> 00:00:29,129
asked for it.

8
00:00:34,601 --> 00:00:35,601
Morning.

9
00:00:36,469 --> 00:00:37,570
Good morning.

10
00:01:59,118 --> 00:02:00,586
If I could,

11
00:02:00,587 --> 00:02:02,689
I'd stay by your side forever,

12
00:02:03,123 --> 00:02:05,225
to make up for all the time we lost.

13
00:02:06,326 --> 00:02:07,026
And then we'll cherish

14
00:02:07,027 --> 00:02:08,862
every single day together.

15
00:02:09,529 --> 00:02:11,364
Is just "cherishing" it enough?

16
00:02:11,865 --> 00:02:14,067
No, it's not. Not even close.

17
00:02:14,868 --> 00:02:17,302
I want our love to keep growing,

18
00:02:17,303 --> 00:02:19,739
until we're the envy of everyone.

19
00:02:20,306 --> 00:02:23,476
Are you really not afraid of anything?

20
00:02:24,577 --> 00:02:26,679
I'm only afraid of losing you.

21
00:02:29,482 --> 00:02:31,850
Falling in love is easy,

22
00:02:31,851 --> 00:02:34,687
but staying in love takes real courage.

23
00:02:35,221 --> 00:02:37,457
And you... you're what keeps me going.

24
00:02:38,424 --> 00:02:40,225
Look at you, such a smooth talker.

25
00:02:40,226 --> 00:02:42,128
You're just trying to
make sure I never leave.

26
00:02:43,329 --> 00:02:45,231
Where would you even go?

27
00:02:45,798 --> 00:02:48,367
Life has its ups and downs, and people...

28
00:02:48,368 --> 00:02:49,968
Hei Mingyan!

29
00:02:49,969 --> 00:02:52,071
Okay, okay... I'll stop. I won't say it.

30
00:03:03,650 --> 00:03:05,752
We'll be together for a long time, right?

31
00:03:07,187 --> 00:03:09,521
As long as you want.

32
00:03:09,522 --> 00:03:11,122
Until the day you don't want me anymore.

33
00:03:11,758 --> 00:03:13,158
Even if I say I don't want you,

34
00:03:13,159 --> 00:03:15,027
you're not allowed to leave.

35
00:03:15,028 --> 00:03:16,461
Wait... that's not right.

36
00:03:16,462 --> 00:03:17,964
How could I ever not want you?

37
00:03:19,098 --> 00:03:22,535
Alright. Whatever you say, I'm yours.

38
00:03:23,303 --> 00:03:26,038
Stop being so romantic all the time.

39
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:28,775
You're making me look
like the heartless one.

40
00:03:29,442 --> 00:03:30,509
Because my whole heart

41
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:32,178
belongs only to you.

42
00:05:12,712 --> 00:05:13,779
For the rest of your life,

43
00:05:13,780 --> 00:05:15,448
you'd better stay right by my side.

44
00:05:15,948 --> 00:05:17,617
I promise.

45
00:05:18,818 --> 00:05:20,819
I love you, my BY.

46
00:05:20,820 --> 00:05:23,523
I love you too, my Bai Bai.
